# RIG data/ — third-party dataset payloads are NOT tracked.
#
# Rationale: the M0 candidate sets are externally licensed and large
# (empa-hipims/hipims_raw.zip alone is 378 MB, well past GitHub's 100 MB
# per-file hard limit). We track *provenance*, not payloads: MANIFEST.md,
# per-dataset README.md, record.json and *.sha256 are enough for a fresh
# clone to re-fetch each source and verify it byte-for-byte.

# Ignore everything under data/ by default...
*

# ...but keep descending into subdirectories so the un-ignores below apply,
# and keep the provenance/licensing files themselves.
!*/
!.gitignore
!MANIFEST.md
!README.md
!LICENSE.txt
!record.json
!*.sha256
